{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e9b99c0863","title":"右派言论——污蔑教学改革  否定学习苏联的成就","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"97374f0856","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"e9b99c0863"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"5841b1c66b","name":"上海财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0e9d39185c","type":"title","text":"右派言论——污蔑教学改革  否定学习苏联的成就","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"ceafc52a8d","type":"authors","text":"上海财经学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"1ac93411b2","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“现在大学生是大学招牌，中学内容，小学教学法。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"0d3b0134f3","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“高校不如中技，要转(学)趁早。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"b51cf16735","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“解放后大学毕业生都要改行。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"5e797bd687","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“我们目前大学生质量不高，初中毕业生也能考取大学。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"d0ad774be5","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)“学校里教书方法太死，把大学生当宝宝，造成我们知识不广，理论和实际脱离，硬搬弄苏联，当然浪费了我们的青春，又受损失。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"c5bd8d49f3","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)“学校里讲苏联课程内容完全不恰当，实际是教条主义。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"4d0d339718","type":"paragraph","text":"(7)“我国学习苏联是教条主义，弄得很多东西(指银行制度)一变再变。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"},{"id":"135ec96118","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《反右派斗争言论选辑　第一辑　学生部份》（中共上海财经学院委员会编，1957年9","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863"}],"page":{"id":"820f200eb6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9b99c0863","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}